UNITED STATES ex rel. Juozas LUBINSKAS, Relator-Appellant, v. Benjamin M. DAY, as Commissioner, etc., Respondent-Appellant. No. 369. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 13, 1930. Ernest Lappano, of New York City, for appellant. John M. Lyons, of New York City, for appellee.

*1020Before L. HAND, AUGUSTUS N.. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed in open court.
